reviewText: This is a great series and I'm glad I have the entire Saiyuki series on DVD! I need Reloaded on DVD then I'm complete!
My second disk skips. I have no idea why hopefully it doesn't happen to yours.

Great addition to anyones collection. This is an amazing show. The animation is good for its time but remember it's an old series so don't expect a "wow" factor but overall I really enjoyed saiyuki, and if yo like action and adventure I would highly recommend you give it a watch :)
I love this series so much. Glad this a complete collection of the full series. Thank you very much for have the series.
